Quick Commerce Dark Store Management System (QCDSMS)

📌 Overview
The Quick Commerce Dark Store Management System (QCDSMS) is a Flask-based cloud solution designed to optimize 
dark store operations through enhanced inventory management, automated order processing, and efficient logistics coordination. 
The system ensures:
-Real-time stock visibility
-Seamless order fulfillment
-Last-mile delivery tracking

🛠️ Tools & Technologies Used
Development Stack
-Programming Language: Python (Flask)
-Database: SQLite
-Frontend: HTML, CSS (Jinja2 Templates)
-Version Control: Git & GitHub
-Deployment Platform (Planned): AWS / Heroku
-Testing Framework: Pytest  

📦 Package Dependencies
The project requires the following packages:
bash
pip install flask sqlite3
